description: For those of you who just joined Rutgers, congratulations on your accomplishment! We’re excited to have you here. Today's meeting will focus on introducing you to the Venture Capital Club, our mission, and the opportunities we offer to help you explore the world of startups, venture investing, and entrepreneurship. We'll cover upcoming events, ways to get involved, and how you can start building your network and skill set early in your college journey. Whether you're new to venture capital or already passionate about startups, RVCC is a place to learn, connect, and grow. We’re looking forward to an amazing year together!
name: Welcome to Rutgers University Venture Capital Club
organizationName: Venture Capital Club of Rutgers University
